Citation.sAbstract: Solid-liquid equilibria (SLE) for the four binary systems of 1-methoxy-2-propanol and 2-butoxy ehtanol with benzene and cyclohexane have been measured by a visual method. For correlating the experimental SLE data, the entahlpy of fusion for 1-methoxy-2-propanol has been measured additionally using a Tian-Calvet batch calorimeter. For the description of the SLE data, the Wilson equation has been used with good results. The SLE data were also compared with prdicted data using modified UNIFAC (Dortmund).
Citation.sTitle: Solid-Liquid Equilibria for Binary Organic Systems Containing 1-Methoxy-2-propanol and 2-Butoxy Ethanol
